Template: redmine-mail2ticket/enviroment
Type: select
Choices: production,development
Description: application environment
 Usualy production or testing

Template: redmine-mail2ticket/project
Type: string
Description: redmine project name 
 Which project have to handle this mailbox ?

Template: redmine-mail2ticket/method
Type: select
Choices: imap,pop
Description: mail address of icinga admin 
 Or simply press enter to use auto genrated name

